; 12.5 km Global EASE-Grid-2.0 grid parameter definition.
; This projection uses the WGS84 ellipsoid.
; The left and right edges of the grid are at -+180.000000 deg longitude.
; The top and bottom edges of the grid are at  +-84.439790 deg latitude.
; This grid exactly nests in the EASE2_M25km grid
; 2011-02-08 : Original grid defined with scale = 12512.63000405 m
; 2014-03-05 : Scale revised to 12512.63000 m
;              Original scale at higher precision was causing accumulated round-off
;              error that resulted in left edge (col=-0.5) values to return
;              longitude 180.0, and right edge values to return longitude -180.0. 
Map Projection:                     Cylindrical Equal-Area (ellipsoid)
Map Reference Latitude:             0.0
Map Reference Longitude:            0.0
Map Second Reference Latitude:      30.0
Map Rotation:                       0.0
