Map Eccentricity:                   0.081819190843   ; wgs84
Map Origin X:                       -17367530.44     ; Grid Map Units Per Cell *
                                                     ; Grid Width / 2
Map Origin Y:                       7307375.92       ; Grid Map Units per Cell *
                                                     ; Grid Height / 2
Grid Map Origin Column:             -0.5
Grid Map Origin Row:                -0.5
Grid Map Units per Cell:            12512.63000      ; meters (see comment)
Grid Width:                         2776
Grid Height:                        1168

